stories.title: 90% of Rails N+1 queries solved with a drop-in fix

stories.text:
Perhaps some of you hang out here, but I just wanted to say I love your product and your vision. I've been playing with it over the last few days, and it feels like a game changer in terms of being able to rapidly turn out little web app experiments I do all the time but don't have the patience to make public and accessible online.

Lowcode/nocode is going to democratize so much of development, allowing so many more people to do it, but from my perspective an equally big benefit is hopefully a massive increase great interactive content that help showcase all these amazing emerging technologies, especially in generative AI.

Lastly, they gave me some of the best customer service I have ever experienced. Truly above and beyond. YC, you guys have a real jem here!
